{"tid":2083191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有報道指若通過港區國安法　日本將對中國表達「遺憾」","createTime":"2020-06-28T14:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T04:32:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"79ed39ed56d620a089b25ce4ded1de0c18599d4e","tid":2083191,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534513-20200628.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534513-20200628.htm&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8filxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=0cac6a8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534513-20200628.htm&h=5b71eca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534513-20200628.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n日本《讀賣新聞》報道，若中國全國人大常委會通過「港區國安法」的實施法案，將會向中國表達「遺憾」，是日本政府僅次於「譴責」的第2嚴厲外交表現，據報日本政府已就此進入協調階段。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，日本在香港大約有1400間企業，日本政府高層官員認為，若法案通過，會動搖香港的高度自治，日本亦屬於當事一方。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，日本政府以往對中國公務船駛入日本聲稱的釣魚島「領海」等涉及國家利益情況時，大多會使用「遺憾」。不過，對於好似港區國安法的外國政策，日本政府若使用「遺憾」一詞將十分罕見。"},{"pid":"723b7b1ed561ec71ae7a8285a5d42acdd4ecbb66","tid":2083191,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"日本同韓國都係想食兩邊飯"},{"pid":"0a264429e177ce4605bccfe5a8a287acd59bf3c1","tid":2083191,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"始終1000萬人民幣遊客對日本太吸引"},{"pid":"2a5368ef776f9b9a2eefb8c0d94c3101955a9ef0","tid":2083191,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"723b7b1ed561ec71ae7a8285a5d42acdd4ecbb66","tid":2083191,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"日本同韓國都係想食兩邊飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:56:55.000Z","msg":"想問下將香港問題推到登野城尖閣級<br />\n<br />\n咁都算係食兩邊茶飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f0babae0bf2ef32341a